Tsunami a Indonesia da girgizar kasa da ta lalata tsibiri, ta kashe mutane 100
Bayan girgizar kasa ta Lombok, an ce ba a bukatar kungiyoyin masu zaman kansu.
Kodayake sama da kashi 10 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen Lombok sun rasa muhallinsu, babu sanarwar bala'i na kasa wanda shine abin da ake bukata kafin a fara neman taimakon agaji daga kasashen duniya.
Sumbung ta ce "da rashin alheri, a lokuta da dama sun bayyana sarai cewa ba su nemi taimakon kasa da kasa ba, don haka yana da ɗan ƙalubale".
Yayin da kungiyar Save the Children ke tattara tawagar da za ta kai hari Palu, ba a tabbatar da ko jami'an kasashen waje za su iya yin aiki a filin ba.
Sutopo, mai magana da yawun hukumar bada agajin bala'i ta kasa, ya ce hukumomin Indonesia na tantance halin da ake ciki a Palu don ganin ko za a ba wa rundunar kasa da kasa damar ba da gudummawa wajen taimakawa.
Tun da girgizar kasa na faruwa a Indonesia a kai a kai, kasar ta kasa shirya kanta don bala'in yanayi.
Yayin da ake gina mafaka a Aceh, ba a iya ganin su daga sauran bakin teku.
Rashin faɗakarwar annobar a Palu duk da faɗakarwar da aka bayar ya haifar da mutuwar mutane.
A lokacin mafi kyau, yawancin tsibirai a Indonesia suna ɗaukar tafiya tsakanin tsibirai da ƙalubale.
Bala'i na kawo matsaloli masu yawa a harkar sufuri.
Jirgin asibiti da ke aiki a Lombok don kula da wadanda girgizar kasa ta shafa yana kan hanyarsa zuwa Palu, amma zai dauki akalla kwanaki uku kafin ya isa sabon wurin da bala'in ya auku.
Shugaba Joko Widodo ya gyara ragowar kayayyakin more rayuwa na Indonesia don kamfen dinsa na zabe kuma ya kashe kudade masu yawa a kan hanyoyi da hanyoyin jirgin kasa.
Amma rashin kudade ya haifar da matsala a cikin gwamnatin Joko wanda zai fuskanci sabon zabe a shekara mai zuwa.
Joko ya kuma fuskanci matsin lamba daga tashin hankali game da rabuwa a cikin Indonesia inda yawancin membobin musulmi suka karɓi imani a cikin tsarin mai kiyayewa.
Fiye da mutane 1,000 aka kashe kuma 10 cikin 1,000 aka raba daga gidajensu kamar yadda kungiyoyin Kirista da Musulmai suka yi fada a gefen titi, da wuka, da bindigogi, da sauran makamai.
Duba: Daniel Sturridge daga Liverpool ya shiga wasan kusa da Chelsea
Daniel Sturridge ya kare Liverpool daga cin Chelsea a Premier Leauge da kwallo a minti na 89 a ranar Asabar a Stamford Bridge a London.
Sturridge ya karbi kwallo daga Xherdan Shaqiri a wajen mil 30 daga kofar Chelsea inda tawagarsa ke kan gaba da 1-0.
Ya sannu a hankali ya buga kwallon a hannun hagu kafin ya harba kwallon zuwa ga kusurwar ƙofar.
Kwallan da aka yi wasa da shi yana tashi sama da yankin fansa yayin da yake hawa zuwa kusurwar dama ta sama.
A ƙarshe, ƙwallon ya ratsa Kepa Arrizabalaga da ke tsalle-tsalle, kuma ya shiga cikin raga.
"Abin da nake yi shi ne na shiga cikin wannan matsayi, na kama kwallon, kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq suna taka leda a gaba kamar yadda zan iya, sannan na yi kokarin samun lokaci mai yawa don kaina", in ji Sturridge a LiverpoolFC.com.
Na ga Kante yana gudu yana neman mataki daya, ban ma yi tunani sosai ba sai na yanke shawarar harba shi.
Chelsea ta yi nasara da ci 1-0 a rabin lokaci bayan da Eden Hazard ya ci kwallo a minti na 25.
Dan wasan Blues ya mayar wa Mateo Kovacic da takalminsa a wasan kafin ya yi ta zura kwallo daga tsakiya ya shiga Liverpool.
Kovacic ya karɓi ƙwallo kuma ya ba da sauri daga tsakiya.
Sai ya yi wani babban wasa wanda ya sa Hazard ya shiga filin wasa.
Hazard ya tsallake 'yan adawa kuma ya buga kwallon da ƙafafun hagu zuwa gabar tsakiya ta nesa ta hanyar Alisson Becker daga Liverpool.
Liverpool za ta fafata da Napoli a wasan rukuni na gasar zakarun Turai a karfe 3 na yammacin Laraba a Stadio San Paolo a Naples, Italiya.
Chelsea za ta kara da Videoton a gasar UEFA Europa a karfe 3 na yammacin Alhamis a London.
An samu karin mutane 832 da suka mutu sakamakon ambaliyar da ta afku a Indonesia
Hukumar kula da bala'i ta kasa ta ce a safiyar Lahadi, adadin wadanda suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da kuma tsunami a Indonesia ya kai 832.
An ruwaito cewa mutane da dama na cikin gine-gine da suka rushe sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 da ta afkawa kasar a ranar Juma'a, inda ta haifar da ambaliyar ruwa mai tsawon kafa 20, in ji kakakin rundunar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho a cikin wata sanarwa.
An rarraba Palu, wanda ke da yawan mutane sama da 380,000, tare da sharar gidaje da suka rushe.
