A cewar majiyoyin yanayi, Hurricane Rosa na raguwa yayin da yake motsawa cikin ruwan sanyi a gabar tekun arewacin Mexico.
Duk da haka, Rosa zai haifar da ruwan sama mai yawa a arewacin Mexico da kudu maso yammacin Amurka a cikin 'yan kwanaki.
Rosa tana da iska mai karfin kilomita 85 a awa daya, kuma ta zama guguwa ta 1 a karfe 5 na safe a ranar Lahadi a yankin gabas kuma tana da nisan mil 385 kudu maso yammacin Punta Eugenia, Mexico.
