Turai ta kai 10-6 zuwa Ryder Cup ranar karshe
Turai za ta iya shiga ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan ta tashi daga wasan hudu da hudu na ranar Asabar da ci gaban Amurka da maki 10-6.
Abokan Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun sami kwarin gwiwa a matsayin shugabannin gasar tare da cin nasara sau biyu a kan Tiger Woods wanda ke ƙoƙarin hawa teburin da ya gabata a Le Golf National a cikin hudu.
