Raymond So, ɗan California mai shekara 19 da ke nazarin kimiyyar halittu da kuma kimiyyar lissafi, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara takardar karatu sa'ad da ya shiga ɗaya daga cikin ɗakunansa a shekarar da ta gabata a lokacin da yake cikin shekara ta farko a Harvard.
