Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia
A cewar rahotanni na hukuma, an kashe mutane 384 sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami mai karfin gaske da ta afkawa garin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda matsalar sadarwa, jami'an tsaro ba su iya samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala da ke arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5.
Fiye da mutane 16,000 ne suka yi gudun hijira bayan bala'in da ya auku a Palu.
Ga wasu abubuwa game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi, wanda ke bakin tekun yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Garin na Shanghai yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwar sa yayin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka afku.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai tsawon kilomita 300 (180 mi) a arewacin Sulawesi.
Regency, wanda shine ƙananan yanki na lardin, yana da yawan mutane 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Farin gona da noma sune babban tattalin arzikin yankin Sulawesi, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Ma'adinan Nickel ma suna da mahimmanci a lardin amma galibi suna cikin Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da ambaliyar tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Ma'aikatar Kula da Bala'in Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A 1938, mutane sama da 200 suka mutu kuma an lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami na yammacin Donggala a 1996 ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana fama da girgizar kasa.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a shekarar da ta gabata:
2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Oktoba, wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin tsibirin Sumatra. Aukuwa ta afku a kasashe 14, inda mutane 226,000 suka mutu a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a gabar yammacin Sumatra a karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu.
Mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar Sumatra.
2006: A kudancin tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a Indonesia, girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa yankin, ta haifar da guguwa mai karfin ruwa a gabar tekun kudu, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta yamma.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 sun mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 a tsibirin Mentawai ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata gidaje goma kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a Pidie Jaya a Aceh ta haifar da bala'i da tashin hankali ga jama'a saboda sun yi ta tuno da asarar rayuka da girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Ba a sami wani hatsari ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu daga ginin.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok amma galibi a arewacin tsibirin inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a tsibirin na wucin gadi.
