Don yanke hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya yi niyyar kashe dukkan wadanda aka kashe da kuma cutar da su, a cewar sanarwar da aka bayar a hukuncin kisa a yankin kudancin New York.
Dukkanin laifuffukan na da hukuncin kisa, bisa ga hukuncin da kotu ta yanke.
Makonni bayan harin, ofishin attorney na tarayya na Amurka ya gabatar da tuhuma 22 ga Saipov wanda ya kunshi kashe mutane takwas da taimakon magudi, wanda a kullum ake amfani da shi a matsayin babban laifi na Amurka a kan aikata laifuka da tashin hankali da kuma lalata motoci.
Harin zai bukaci "shirye-shiryen da aka yi a cikin al'ada da kuma tsinkaya a gaba", in ji mai gabatar da kara, wanda ya bayyana yanayin ayyukan Saipov a matsayin "m, mai zalunci da rashin hankali".
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi sanadin rashin lafiya, hatsari da kuma asarar dangi da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, kamar yadda jihar ta sanar.
Wadanda aka kashe biyar ne masu yawon bude ido daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan tun lokacin da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a kudancin New York.
An yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa a kan kisan magunguna guda biyu, amma daga bisani aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
Hukuncin kisa na ƙarshe a New York shine shari'ar Julius da Ethel Rosenberg a 1953, an kashe ma'aurata biyu bayan an yanke musu hukuncin laifin ba da rahoto ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe su duka a kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, ɗan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin hankali a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa mai binciken cewa ya san abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya gaya wa jami'an da ke jagorantar cewa ya yi kokarin kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayar salula, a cewar karar.
'Yan sanda sun kara da cewa ya kuma nemi a saka tutar ISIS a dakinsa a asibiti.
Ya yi ikirarin cewa ba shi da laifi a kan zarge-zarge 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu gabatar da kara na Saipov, ya ce sun yi matukar takaici da hukuncin da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
Patton ya ce, "Muna ganin hukuncin kisa maimakon rai da rai a gidan yari ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba zai kara tsawaita sakamakon wannan lamarin ga duk wanda ya shiga cikin lamarin".
Lauyoyin Saipov sun nemi mai gabatar da kara da ya hana hukuncin kisa.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin Tory ya ce ya kamata a dauki nauyin tattaunawar Brexit a kan NIGEL FARAGE
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "sanya sojojin jama'a" a yau yayin zanga-zangar taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce dole ne 'yan siyasa su "yi murna" da 'yan Eurosceptics - daya daga cikin 'yan majalisar Theresa May da suka shawarce shi da ya dauki nauyin tattaunawar da Tarayyar Turai.
Shugaban 'yanci Peter Bone ya ce za a yi tafiyar 'yanci a Birnin Birmingham na Ingila a yanzu idan Farage ya zama sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Maye ke fuskanta wajen tabbatar da rabuwa da shi ya kara daukaka ne yayin da 'yan Tories suka shiga zanga-zangar adawa da Brexit a birnin.
Firayim Minista yana ta kokarin ganin an aiwatar da shirin Chequers a yayin da ake fuskantar hare-hare daga Brexit, wanda ya tsira da Tarayyar Turai.
Kungiyar ta tabbatar da cewa zai ci gaba da kokarinsa na adawa da yarjejeniyar da Brussels duk da fushinsa - kuma ya tilasta wa 'yan Eurosceptics da ma'aikata su zabi tsakanin abin da ya dace da kuma 'yancinsa.
Bone ya ce yana nufin ya yi murabus daga taron Solihull yana son 'dakatar da Chequers'.
Ya ba da shawarar cewa Farage ya kamata ya yi shawarwari tare da abokan aikinsa kuma ya dauki alhakin tattaunawa da Brussels.
'Idan ya kasance a cikin alhakin, za mu tafi yanzu,' ya ce.
'Yan majalisar Wellingborough sun kara da cewa: 'Zan tsaya kan ficewar daga Tarayyar Turai amma muna bukatar mu dakatar da Checkers.'
Da yake bayyana adawarsa ga Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: 'Ba mu yi yaƙi ba a duniya don mu zama bayi.
Muna son kafa dokokinmu a kasarmu.
Bone ya yi watsi da shawarar cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun lokacin zaben 2016: 'ra'ayin cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza kuma har yanzu suna son kiyaye labarin ba daidai ba.'
Tory Brexiteer Andrea Jenkyns a cikin wannan zanga-zangar ta gaya wa manema labarai: 'Ina cewa a sauƙaƙe: Firayim Minista, saurari mutane.
'Yan Cheka ba su da sha'awa ga jama'a, 'yan adawa ba su zabe su ba, ba su gamsu da jam'iyyarmu ba, kuma masu fafutukarmu sun cika tituna, kuma sun sa mu zama na farko a zaben.
'Ka sauke Chequers ɗin ka fara sauraro.'
A cikin wata sanarwa da ta rubuta ga May, ta kara da cewa: "Firai ministan ya ci gaba da aiki idan 'yan Houthi sun cika alkawuransu".
Farage ya ce ya kamata 'yan siyasa su ji 'farin ciki' idan suna shirin yin la'akari da sakamakon kuri'ar raba gardama ta 2016.
"Yanzu batun amincewa ne tsakaninmu - jama'a da 'yan siyasarmu", in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin hana Brexit, kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu cewa 'ba za mu bari ku fita ku yi hakan ba.'
A cikin jawabinsa ga taron masu sha'awar, ya kara da cewa: 'Ina son yin nazarin siyasa game da mu, wanda ke da sha'awar Brexit, yana jin daɗi.
"Muna ƙarfafa sojojin mutanen wannan ƙasa su ci nasara a kan Brexit kuma ba za mu daina ba har sai mun zama masu 'yancin kai, masu cin gashin kansu, masu alfahari da Burtaniya".
A halin yanzu, magoya bayan sun yi gangamin a Birmingham kafin taron na tsawon sa'o'i biyu a cikin gari.
Ayyukan 'yan gwagwarmayar sun yi tasiri a kan Tories Against Brexit bayan ƙaddamar da ƙungiyar a ƙarshen wannan makon.
Ma'aikatan Lord Adonis sun zargi masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kan matsalolin tsaro da suka fuskanta da jam'iyyun lokacin da suka bude taron.
'Waɗannan su ne mutanen da suka gaya mana cewa za su iya samun tsarin IT da duk fasahar zamani don Kanada da ƙari, don iyakoki marasa ƙyama, cinikin kyauta ba tare da iyaka ba a Ireland,' in ji shi.
'Wannan abu ne mai ban dariya.
Babu wani abu mai kyau game da Brexit, "ya kara da cewa.
