Dundee Stars ta koma gasar Elite League ranar Juma'a ta rasa Belfast Giants daga cin kofin wasan 5-3 a Dundee ranar Asabar.
Giants sun ci gaba da cin kwallaye biyu ta hanyar bugun da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier suka yi.
