Kamfanin jirgin sama na Air Niugini ya ce mutum ya bace bayan jirgin Lagoon
Kamfanin jirgin ya yi jirgin da ya fadi cikin Tekun Fasifik a Micronesia; yanzu an ce kafin jirgin ya nutse cikin tekun. Mutum daya ya bace bayan an ceto fasinjoji 47 da ma'aikatan jirgin ba tare da an yi musu rauni ba.
Kamfanin jiragen sama na Air Niugini ya ce: "Ba a ga wani mutum ba a ranar Asabar kafin a saki wadanda aka kashe.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce: "Mun yi aiki tare da hukumomin yankin; asibiti da kuma rukunin bincike don gano mutumin.
Kamfanin jirgin bai ba da cikakken bayani game da shekarun da kuma asalin fasinjan ba.
Bayan jirgin ya fadi a bakin ruwa; yayin da yake kokarin sauka a filin jirgin saman Chuuk Island; jirgin ruwa na gida ya ceci fasinjoji da sauran ma'aikatan jirgin.
Rahotanni sun ce a ranar Juma'a an kai fasinjoji bakwai asibiti.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ruwaito cewa a ranar Asabar, fasinjoji shida ne ke asibiti kuma dukkansu suna cikin koshin lafiya.
Dalilin da ya sa jirgin ya fadi da kuma abubuwan da suka biyo baya ba a bayyana ba.
Kamfanin jiragen sama na Amurka da rundunar sojin sama na Amurka sun ce jirgin ya yi gajeren sauka a filin jirgin sama na Lagoon.
Shaidu sun ruwaito cewa jirgin yana kokarin dakatar da gudu a filin jirgin sama.
Wani fasinja dan Amurka mai suna Bill Jaynes ya ce: "Yaron ya yi kasa sosai.
"Wannan abu ne mai kyau", in ji Jaynes.
Jaynes ya ce shi da sauran fasinjojin suna shirin tafiya cikin ruwa mai zurfi zuwa hanyar gaggawa ta jirgin da ke nutsewa.
Ya ce: "Ma'aikatan jirgin sun yi rikici, sun kasa kame kansu, sun yi ihu, kuma hakan ya sa ya ji rauni kadan a kansa".
Sojojin ruwan Amurka sun ce masu aikin gida da ke aiki a kusa da tashar jirgin sun taimaka ta hanyar amfani da jirgin ruwa mai saukar ungulu don kwashe fasinjoji kafin jirgin ya nutse zuwa zurfin mita 30 (100 feet) a cikin teku.
Bayanai daga cibiyar tsaro ta jirgin sama sun nuna cewa a cikin shekaru biyu da suka gabata, fasinjoji 111 na kamfanonin jiragen sama da ke da rajistar PNG sun mutu sakamakon hatsarin jirgin sama; amma duk waɗannan ba su da alaƙa da Air Niugini.
Masu bincike sun bayyana abin da ya faru a daren da aka ƙone matan.
