Mai bincike Paul Rowlett a ma'aikatar shari'a ta Amurka ya yi amfani da sa'o'i da dama wajen tantance hujjojin da aka samu a filin da lamarin ya faru.
Ya ba da cikakkun bayanai ga kotun hukuma game da yadda ya yi amfani da bayanan wayar salula don gano motsi na wanda ake tuhuma Quinton Tellis, mai shekaru 29, da kuma wanda aka azabtar, Jessica Chambers, mai shekaru 19, a daren da aka kashe ta.
