Labarai game da Red Tide: yana faruwa a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani sabon rahoto daga Hukumar Kula da Kifi da namun daji ya nuna cewa raguwar Red Tide yana faruwa a wani ɓangare na Tampa Bay.
A cewar rahoton FWC, yanayin raunin daji ya faru ne a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier - wanda ke nuna cewa akwai raguwa mai ban mamaki.
Fure-fure a cikin Red Tide ya yadu a cikin wani yanki mai nisan mil 130 na bakin teku daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin Lee Community.
Ana iya samun patches a cikin mil 10 daga gabar tekun na al'ummar Hillsborough amma an sami wasu wurare a makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da Red Tide a cikin al'ummar Pasco.
An riga an ba da rahoton abubuwan da ke faruwa a cikin ko a gefen tekun na al'ummar Pinellas a cikin makon da ya gabata; ƙananan abubuwan da ke faruwa a cikin yankin Hillsborough; da kuma ƙaruwa a cikin yankin Manatee da matsakaici zuwa babban abin da ke faruwa a cikin al'ummar Charlotte da kuma babban abin da ke faruwa a cikin ko a gefen tekun a cikin Lee da ƙananan abubuwan da ke faruwa a cikin al'ummar Collier.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni a cikin al'ummomin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier.
A makon da ya gabata; ba a sami rahoton wani abu ba a yankin arewa maso yammacin Florida.
